cerca de 35 decibéis

1116
01:20:27,102 --> 01:20:29,470
e analisar as respostas
neurais.

1117
01:20:29,472 --> 01:20:31,038
É alto?

1118
01:20:31,040 --> 01:20:32,708
Dentro do campo auditivo normal.

1119
01:20:34,877 --> 01:20:36,145
Tá bom.

1120
01:20:36,745 --> 01:20:37,947
Vamos lá.

