1399
01:47:02,005 --> 01:47:03,071
O que tá acontecendo?

1400
01:47:03,073 --> 01:47:04,706
Flashes da primeira luta,

1401
01:47:04,708 --> 01:47:06,808
mas Drago está demonstrando
cautela dessa vez.

1402
01:47:06,810 --> 01:47:08,179
-Tá bem?
-Sim, tô bem.

1403
01:47:08,182 --> 01:47:09,182
E Creed fica de pé.

1404
01:47:09,266 --> 01:47:10,266
Nocauteie ele!

1405
01:47:11,348 --> 01:47:14,649
